    "description": "<strong>Witch Guild Survivor</strong> is a fun horde roguelite game where you play as a witch that must survive from the monsters using your poweful spells! Collect white orbs and upgrade your magic spells. Choose a combination of various elements to generate synergies between them in each run. Let's have some fun in this horde survival game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163310/extras/f2c4a45a44826b1461f220053bdadbda.poster.avif?t=1665682376\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163310/extras/f2c4a45a44826b1461f220053bdadbda.webm?t=1665682376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163310/extras/f2c4a45a44826b1461f220053bdadbda.mp4?t=1665682376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Variety Builds Every Run</strong><br>In this roguelite survival game, you can choose a combination of various elements to generate synergies between them in each run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163310/extras/843a168362b5ca34adb5f90ce3600f4a.poster.avif?t=1665682376\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163310/extras/843a168362b5ca34adb5f90ce3600f4a.webm?t=1665682376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2163310/extras/843a168362b5ca34adb5f90ce3600f4a.mp4?t=1665682376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Select Your Witch, Wand and Spell</strong><br>Choose from the witches, wands and spells available in this demo version. Each combination generates a different game experience.<br><br>{